nr_to_lte_sql: DECLARE @DATETIME_ID varchar(50)=DATETIME_VALUE , @UNIQUE_ID varchar(500)=UNIQUE_ID_VALUE select cast(ROUND(100*(sum(pmHoPrepSuccOutEutran) / sum(pmHoPrepAttOutEutran)) * (sum(pmHoExeSuccOutEutran) / sum(pmHoExeAttOutEutran)),2) as numeric(36,2)) as KPIValue from DC_E_NR_NRCELLCU_RAW where NR_NAME=@UNIQUE_ID AND DATE_ID=@DATETIME_ID
en_dc_intra: DECLARE @DATETIME_ID varchar(50)=DATETIME_VALUE , @UNIQUE_ID varchar(500)=UNIQUE_ID_VALUE select cast(ROUND(100*(sum(pmEndcPSCellChangeSuccIntraSgnb) / sum(pmEndcPSCellChangeSuccIntraSgnb)),2) as numeric(36,2)) as KPIValue from DC_E_NR_NRCELLCU_RAW where NR_NAME=@UNIQUE_ID AND DATE_ID=@DATETIME_ID
en_dc_inter: DECLARE @DATETIME_ID varchar(50)=DATETIME_VALUE , @UNIQUE_ID varchar(500)=UNIQUE_ID_VALUE select cast(ROUND(100*(sum(pmEndcPSCellChangeSuccInterSgnb) / sum(pmEndcPSCellChangeAttInterSgnb)),2) as numeric(36,2)) as KPIValue from DC_E_NR_NRCELLCU_RAW where NR_NAME=@UNIQUE_ID AND DATE_ID=@DATETIME_ID
ul_packet_loss: DECLARE @DATETIME_ID varchar(50)=DATETIME_VALUE , @UNIQUE_ID varchar(500)=UNIQUE_ID_VALUE select cast(ROUND(100*(sum(pmPdcpPktLossUlQos) - sum(pmPdcpPktRecUlOooQos) / sum(pmPdcpPktRecUlQos) + sum(pmPdcpPktLossUlToQos) - sum(pmPdcpPktLossUlToDiscQos) + sum(pmPdcpPktRecUlOooQos)),2) as numeric(36,2)) as KPIValue from DC_E_VPP_RPUSERPLANELINK_V_RAW where NE_NAME=@UNIQUE_ID AND DATE_ID=@DATETIME_ID
dl_packet_loss: DECLARE @DATETIME_ID varchar(50)=DATETIME_VALUE , @UNIQUE_ID varchar(500)=UNIQUE_ID_VALUE select cast(ROUND(100*(sum(pmPdcpPktRecDlDisc5qi) - sum(pmPdcpPktRecDlDiscAqm5qi)) / sum( pmPdcpPktRecDl5qi),2) as numeric(8,2)) as KPIValue from DC_E_VPP_S1ULINK_V_RAW where NR_NAME=@UNIQUE_ID AND DATE_ID=@DATETIME_ID
differentiated_average_ul: DECLARE @DATETIME_ID varchar(50)=DATETIME_VALUE , @UNIQUE_ID varchar(500)=UNIQUE_ID_VALUE select cast(ROUND(100*(sum(pmFlexLcgThpVolUl) / sum(pmFlexLcgThpTimeUl/1000)),2) as numeric(8,2)) as KPIValue from DC_E_ERBS_EUTRANCELLFDD_FLEX_RAW UNION select cast(ROUND(100*(sum(pmFlexLcgThpVolUl) / sum(pmFlexLcgThpTimeUl/1000)),2) as numeric(8,2)) as KPIValue from DC_E_ERBS_EUTRANCELLTDD_FLEX_RAW where NR_NAME=@UNIQUE_ID AND DATE_ID=@DATETIME_ID
